title: Largest Ecuadorian-American population groups in the U.S. , by county 2010
summary: This chart shows the Largest Ecuadorian-American population in the groups competirion .
\\n From the chart we see that the Bronx_County_NY Population made the Largest number by some margin , with only 17638 .
Kings_County_NJ and Queens_County_NY made a respectable 28684 and 98512 number , with Suffolk_County_NY and Essex_County_NJ not far behind , at 17638 and 25169 respectively .
gold: This statistic depicts the largest Ecuadorian-American population groups living in different counties across the United States as of 2010 . At this time there were 98,512 people of Ecuadorian origin living in Queens County in New York .
